title: Auburn holds off rival Bama in top-2 showdown
description: Johni Broome had 19 points to lead six Auburn players in double figures, and Auburn held off Alabama 94-85 in a No. 1 vs. No. 2 showdown Saturday.

title: Ex-White Sox All-Star Jenks has stomach cancer
description: Bobby Jenks, a two-time All-Star closer and World Series champion with the Chicago White Sox, is being treated for stomach cancer.

title: Man City rediscover flair as Merino steps up for Arsenal
'We are not going to stop' - Arteta fires title race warning to Liverpool
description: Mikel Arteta has warned Liverpool that Arsenal are "not going to stop" fighting for the Premier League title after securing a late win against Leicester City, four days after Arne Slot's side dropped points to Everton.

title: 'What a week' - in-form Everton's revival under Moyes keeps rolling
description: No Premier League team has picked up more points than Everton since David Moyes returned to Goodison Park in January.

title: 'He can smell danger' - is Merino Arsenal's striker solution?
description: Mikel Merino makes his case to be Arsenal's striker solution after his match-winning heroics in the vital victory at Leicester, says BBC Sport chief football writer Phil McNulty.

title: Follow live: What time is it? NBA All-Star Saturday Night's big events are here
description: The action starts at 8 p.m. ET with the Skills Challenge, then Dame aims for a 3-Point Contest trifecta before Mac McClung tries to throw down a Slam Dunk 3-peat.
author: Yahoo Sports

title: NBA All-Star 2025: Stephen Curry makes spectacular backward, no-look half-court shot at practice
description: Curry was having fun during NBA All-Star practice and maybe reminded the league that H-O-R-S-E should be part of the weekend.
author: Yahoo Sports
